column8: This was a small update to the crate which has to do with Rust language features and compiler versions, no substantial changes.
No major changes in the crate, mostly updates to use new nightly Rust features.

Refactors the `offset_of` macros to optionally replace their existing `unsafe`
implementations with the unstable internal `core::mem::offset_of` macro. The
existing `unsafe` implementations are unaltered.
